22
00:01:10,745 --> 00:01:11,025
Okay.

23
00:01:17,490 --> 00:01:21,073
[SPEAKER_12]: The next item is to revisit public participation procedures.

24
00:01:21,173 --> 00:01:28,358
[SPEAKER_12]: When we had early on in the process, we had voted to save public participation until the end of meetings.

25
00:01:29,358 --> 00:01:41,107
[SPEAKER_12]: And it's been suggested that we change, that we consider changing that to have public participation after each agenda discussion item.

26
00:01:43,248 --> 00:01:44,229
[SPEAKER_12]: Any discussion on that?

27
