[SPEAKER_11]: And there might be other things that come up as we're talking about other topics.

39
00:02:59,365 --> 00:03:13,452
[SPEAKER_11]: I thought it would have been very helpful to have had her feedback and input and suggestions when we were talking about the topic at hand, rather than later when we had disposed of the topic.

40
00:03:14,367 --> 00:03:24,575
