370
00:32:39,913 --> 00:32:57,183
[SPEAKER_12]: So, you know, we maybe will need to extend it somewhat, but my hope was that while we don't have the call-in center for the summer, they're going to rejoin us in the fall, that we would take time and hash out sort of the sort of overarching issues.

