[SPEAKER_12]: I feel like Anthony, you can't access the Google folder necessarily, right?

849
01:21:09,900 --> 01:21:11,321
[SPEAKER_12]: So I'm trying to send them to you.

850
01:21:11,721 --> 01:21:17,324
[SPEAKER_12]: I'm sending them to you individually, but has everyone been able to access the Google folder?

851
01:21:17,384 --> 01:21:22,066
[SPEAKER_12]: And that's where we're dropping all the sort of reports from the interviews.

852
01:21:23,738 --> 01:21:37,808
[SPEAKER_12]: Um, and so far we've done Nina Nazarian, Zach bears, the mayor, uh, Jenny Graham, Jenny Graham.

853
01:21:37,868 --> 01:21:38,308
[SPEAKER_12]: Thank you.

854
01:21:39,329 --> 01:21:42,591
[SPEAKER_12]: And Alicia hunt, but I haven't finished that report yet.

855
01:21:42,631 --> 01:21:43,772
[SPEAKER_12]: It'll be in the folder soon.

856
01:21:45,253 --> 01:21:51,437
[SPEAKER_12]: Um, so what I guess I'm, so I just, I wanted to sort of touch base on that.

857
01:21:52,398 --> 01:21:52,498
[SPEAKER_12]: Um,

858
01:21:54,138 --> 01:21:59,442
[SPEAKER_12]: make sure everybody has access to those that ask if there's any questions on any of the reports.

859
01:21:59,462 --> 01:22:07,368
[SPEAKER_12]: And then I also just wanted to see how the scheduling of the interviews is going.

860
01:22:07,648 --> 01:22:14,914
[SPEAKER_12]: And if anybody's heard back from anybody, Maureen and I are gonna be talking with the city clerk soon.

861
01:22:15,134 --> 01:22:18,497
[SPEAKER_12]: That's the only one right now that I have currently on the books.

862
01:22:21,005 --> 01:22:25,108
[SPEAKER_12]: Um, how, how, and Nicole hopefully is going to get back to Danielle soon.

863
01:22:25,168 --> 01:22:25,608
[SPEAKER_12]: Hopefully.

864
01:22:26,329 --> 01:22:29,251
[SPEAKER_12]: Um, Ron, have you heard from any of the other city councilors?

865
01:22:29,691 --> 01:22:31,372
[SPEAKER_07]: Yeah, I've updated the spreadsheet.

866
01:22:31,432 --> 01:22:33,113
[SPEAKER_07]: I have, I have Kit.

867
01:22:33,434 --> 01:22:34,835
[SPEAKER_07]: Kit Collins is scheduled.

868
01:22:34,855 --> 01:22:47,023
[SPEAKER_07]: Um, Justin saying, uh, George Scarpelli, Rick Carviello are all wait while we waited for the holiday to pass the budget and the holiday to pass.

